name: Suba
overview: Suba is a Bay Area Architecture and Interior Design firm. The firm was created in 1999 by Suanne Bassett AIA, an Architect licensed in California and New York. Suanne worked on large public building projects such as museums, office towers and university buildings before returning to the Bay Area to learn residential and light commercial. This remains the focus of her work today. Suba is collaborative in design and construction, continually exploring new ideas, sustainable materials and cost effective building techniques.
